cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "precis-mcp: Model Context Protocol server for structured document and paper corpus access"
abstract: >-
  precis-mcp is a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that provides AI
  agents with structured, token-efficient access to documents and scientific
  paper corpora. It supports reading, writing, searching, and annotating
  DOCX, LaTeX, Markdown, and PDF files, and exposes a per-chunk semantic
  search interface over ingested papers backed by PostgreSQL + pgvector.
